Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gandaky&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>prostata&nbsp;<b>mahsus
antigen (PCA)&nbsp;</b>- prostat neoplazmasy bilen g&uuml;man
edil&yacute;&auml;n erektil disfunksi&yacute;aly n&auml;saglarda.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksional, radiasi&yacute;a
we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Jyns agzalaryny&#328;&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>ultrases sesli&nbsp;<b>farmakodeprografi&yacute;asy,&nbsp;</b>esasy
erektil disfunksi&yacute;a, &ouml;&#328;ki &#351;ikes &yacute;a-da &ccedil;anak
&yacute;a-da perineal organlarda ge&ccedil;irilen amallar, jyns
agzalaryny&#328; deformasi&yacute;asy, jyns agzalaryny&#328; gan
a&yacute;lany&#351;yny&#328; intensiwligini anyk ultrases barlagydyr.
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly endokrin, akyl we newrologiki n&auml;sazlyklar,
&#351;e&yacute;le hem falloprostetikadan &ouml;&#328; ...&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;kli synag&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
ereksi&yacute;a itergi bermek we gar&#351;ylyk g&ouml;rkezijisini hasaplamak
&uuml;&ccedil;in wazoaktiw dermanlary&#328; jyns agzalaryna girizilmegi.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sa&yacute;lanan penile arteriografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>we&nbsp;<b>kavernosografi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>,
erektil disfunksi&yacute;any&#328; damar tebigatyny a&yacute;yrmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;an rentgen barlag usullarydyr.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gijeki gij&auml;ni&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;megine&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>(jyns
agzalaryny&#328; ulalmagyna) we jyns agzalaryny&#328;&nbsp;<b>berkligine&nbsp;baha
bermek&nbsp;</b>azyndan iki gije amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar, i&#328; azyndan
10% &yacute;a-da ondanam k&ouml;p dowam ed&yacute;&auml;n jyns agzalaryny&#328;
dikelmegi we berkligi azyndan 60% derejesinde bolup ge&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;r.
, erektil mehanizmi&#328; howpsuzlygyny
g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Doly jynsy gatna&#351;yk &uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;eterlik
ereksi&yacute;any dikeltmek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a
bilen i&yacute;mitlenmek, bedeni&#328; agramy, fiziki i&#351;je&#328;lik we
jynsy i&#351;je&#328;lik kadala&#351;&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&yacute;mitde
beloklara, witaminlere we mineral duzlara, bal, tagam, ysly zatlara ba&yacute;
i&yacute;mitler bolmaly.&nbsp;Alkogol i&ccedil;gilerini
&ccedil;&auml;klendirmek we k&auml;bir &yacute;agda&yacute;larda alkogolly
i&ccedil;gileri d&uuml;&yacute;b&uuml;nden ret etmek erkek adamy&#328; erektil
i&#351;ini dikeltm&auml;ge k&ouml;mek ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;N&auml;sagy&#328;
ereksi&yacute;a &yacute;aramaz t&auml;sir edip biljek dermanlaryny
&yacute;atyrmak &yacute;a-da &ccedil;aly&#351;mak m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;iligi
baradaky mesel&auml;ni &ccedil;&ouml;zmeli.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Erektil
disfunksi&yacute;any derman bilen bejermegi&#328; birinji tapgyrynda&nbsp;<i>testosterony&#328;&nbsp;</i>we&nbsp;<i>agyz
erektogen dermanlaryny&#328;&nbsp;(fosfodiesterazy&#328; 5
inhibitory)&nbsp;konsentrasi&yacute;asyny &yacute;okarlandyr&yacute;an&nbsp;</i>dermanlar
ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;Bejergini&#328; ikinji basgan&ccedil;agy,&nbsp;<i>wazaktiw
seri&#351;deleri&nbsp;(prostaglandin E1, fentolamin,&nbsp;papaverin)
intrauretral we / &yacute;a-da i&ccedil;erki administrasi&yacute;any&nbsp;</i>&ouml;z
i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;Androjen &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi bilen,&nbsp;<i>androjeni
&ccedil;aly&#351;mak bejergisi&nbsp;</i>- testosterony&#328; dermanlyk sanjym
we transdermal g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri bilen&nbsp;amala
a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Negativeerli negatiw basy&#351; bejergisi (wakuum enjamlary).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Pes energi&yacute;a &#351;ok tolkun bejergisi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Psihosexoterapi&yacute;a.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a
&uuml;&ccedil;in hirurgiki &ccedil;&auml;reler, &ccedil;anaklyk organlaryna gan
getir&yacute;&auml;n arteri&yacute;alary&#328; lez&yacute;onlary bolan
n&auml;saglar &uuml;&ccedil;in g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu &yacute;agda&yacute;da,
&#351;ikes seb&auml;pli izolirlenen arterial kem&ccedil;ilikli
&yacute;igitlerde i&#328; o&#328;at netijelere gara&#351;yp bolar, umumy aterosklerozly
erkeklerde bolsa, bu amallardan so&#328; t&auml;siri gysga bolar.&nbsp;Erektil
disfunksi&yacute;any bejermegi&#328; be&yacute;leki &auml;hli usullary
&#351;owsuz bolsa we n&auml;sag &ouml;z meselesini&#328;
d&uuml;&yacute;pg&ouml;ter &ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;lmegini talap etse&nbsp;,
ereksi&yacute;any simulirle&yacute;&auml;n &yacute;arym gaty protezler
&yacute;a-da gidrawliki implantlar&nbsp;<i>bilen phaloendoprostetika&nbsp;</i>ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sagdyn durmu&#351;
&yacute;&ouml;relgesine e&yacute;ermek, &auml;hli lukmanlary&#328;
g&ouml;rkezmelerini &yacute;erine &yacute;etirmek, urolog (androlog) bilen
yzygiderli g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek we maslahatla&#351;mak maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Intakyn durmu&#351;dan n&auml;gilelik.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;li stres we depressi&yacute;a.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Toplumlary&#328; &ouml;s&uuml;&#351;i we &ouml;z&uuml;&#328;e
hormat go&yacute;magy&#328; peselmegi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ma&#351;gala &yacute;a-da gatna&#351;yk problemalary.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ouml;nelgesizlik.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Erektil
disfunksi&yacute;any&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351; &ccedil;&auml;releri durmu&#351;y&#328;
kadala&#351;magyny, &yacute;eterlik fiziki i&#351;je&#328;ligi, &ccedil;ilimi
ta&#351;lamagy, alkogol i&ccedil;gilerini&#328; &ccedil;&auml;klendirilmegini,
bedeni&#328; agramyny, gandaky gl&yacute;ukozany we lipidleri, &#351;e&yacute;le
hem adaty jyns durmu&#351;yny &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>So&#328;ky
on&yacute;yllyklarda erektil disfunksi&yacute;any h&auml;zirki zaman ne&#351;e
bejergisi hassalary&#328; k&ouml;p&uuml;sinde &ccedil;aklamany
gowula&#351;dyrdy.&nbsp;Konserwatiw bejergini alyp bilme&yacute;&auml;n erektil
disfunksi&yacute;any&#328; agyr &yacute;agda&yacute;larynda, damar
mikrohirurgiki amallary &yacute;a-da &yacute;okary t&auml;sirli d&ouml;wrebap
implantlary ulanmak bilen funksi&yacute;any dikeltmek m&uuml;mkindir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a n&auml;me seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a &uuml;&ccedil;in konserwatiw bejergi
n&auml;derejede t&auml;sirli?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a &uuml;&ccedil;in fosfodiesteraz 5
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;li ingibitorlary ulanmak &uuml;&ccedil;in ha&yacute;sy
gar&#351;ylyklar bar?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;any&#328; &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykyp
biljek kyn&ccedil;ylyklary ha&yacute;sylar?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a operasi&yacute;asy ha&ccedil;an amala
a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a bilen ereksi&yacute;any doly dikeltmek
m&uuml;mkinmi?</span></p>

